OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FThe Chancellor must plug a #50 billion
OL,7,Fblack hole in the nation's public
OL,8,Ffinances, with at least a 2p hike to
OL,9,Fthe basic rate of income tax likely to
OL,10,Fbe needed, a major economic think tank
OL,11,Fhas warned.
OL,13,FThe National Institute of Economic and
OL,14,FSocial Research (Niesr) has further
OL,15,Fraised the spectre of tax increases at
OL,16,Fthe upcoming November 26 Budget as it
OL,17,Fsaid it believes Rachel Reeves is on
OL,18,Ftrack to miss one of her fiscal rules
OL,19,Fby #38.2 billion in 2029-30.
