OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FThis is before the near-#10 billion
OL,7,Frequired to rebuild the fiscal buffer
OL,8,Fthat has been wiped out, according to
OL,9,Fthe group.
OL,11,FIn it latest economic outlook, Niesr
OL,12,Fsaid it believes the UK's independent
OL,13,Ffiscal watchdog, the Office for Budget
OL,14,FResponsibility (OBR), will predict a
OL,15,Fsmaller deficit of around #20 billion
OL,16,Fwhen its latest forecasts are
OL,17,Fpublished alongside the Budget.
