OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FBut Niesr is calling on the Chancellor
OL,7,Fto aim for a buffer of at least #30
OL,8,Fbillion on top of this to help future-
OL,9,Fproof the finances against further
OL,10,Fshocks, which would still leave her
OL,11,Fneeding to find #50 billion.
OL,13,FIt said the Chancellor will likely
OL,14,Fneed to break her manifesto pledge and
OL,15,Fincrease income tax, rather than
OL,16,F"messing around" with changes to
OL,17,Fmarginal taxes, which it argues would
OL,18,Fbe more damaging to the economy in the
OL,19,Flong run.
