OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FNiesr said a 2p rise on the 20% basic
OL,7,Frate of income tax was expected to be
OL,8,Fthe minimum needed to repair Britain's
OL,9,Fbattered public finances, raising
OL,10,Faround an extra #20 billion.
OL,12,FA 5p rise on the 40% higher rate would
OL,13,Fadd a further #10 billion, with around
OL,14,F#500 million from a similar hike to
OL,15,Fthe upper band, it added.
OL,17,FThis would impact economic growth `
OL,18,Fknocking off around one percentage
OL,19,Fpoint on its forecast for next year to
OL,20,F1.1% in 2026, rising to a 0.3
OL,21,Fpercentage point hit in the third year.
