OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FBut it cautioned the alternatives were
OL,7,Ffar worse, with a rise in VAT pushing
OL,8,Fup inflation as costs are passed on to
OL,9,Fconsumers, while corporation tax hikes
OL,10,F"discourages investment leading to
OL,11,Fpermanently lower GDP".
OL,13,FAnd if credibility in the public
OL,14,Ffinances is not restored, borrowing
OL,15,Fcosts are set to remain high while
OL,16,Fdebt will reach "unsustainable"
OL,17,Flevels, Niesr said.
OL,19,FStephen Millard, deputy director for
OL,20,FMacroeconomics, said Ms Reeves would
OL,21,Fneed to make "brave choices".
