OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FHe said: "She will likely need to
OL,7,Fbreak her manifesto pledge by raising
OL,8,Fincome tax ` rather than attempting to
OL,9,Ffill the gap by messing around with
OL,10,Flots of changes to marginal taxes ` as
OL,11,Fthis would be the least bad option for
OL,12,Fthe economy.
OL,14,F"A mixture of tax rises and spending
OL,15,Fcuts is needed to put the UK economy
OL,16,Fand public finances 'back on track',
OL,17,Fwhich would in turn help the
OL,18,FGovernment to focus on its mission to
OL,19,Fdeliver higher economic growth and
OL,20,Fbetter living standards across the
OL,21,Fcountry."
