OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FMs Reeves had pledged not to raise
OL,7,Ftaxes for working people in Labour's
OL,8,Fgeneral election manifesto ` widely
OL,9,Finterpreted to mean income tax, VAT,
OL,10,Femployee national insurance
OL,11,Fcontributions, and corporation tax.
OL,13,FShe instead raised employers' national
OL,14,Finsurance contributions (NICs) in last
OL,15,Fautumn's budget and said at the time
OL,16,Fshe said would not repeat such a tax-
OL,17,Frising budget "ever again".
