OL,3,CIncome tax hike of at least 2p likely
OL,4,Cneeded to plug Budget hole, warns Niesr
OL,6,FBut she has already set the stage to
OL,7,Frenege on Labour's manifesto pledge,
OL,8,Frefusing to rule out tax hikes in her
OL,9,Fpre-Budget speech on Tuesday and
OL,10,Fwarning "each of us must do our bit".
OL,12,FDavid Aikman, a Niesr director, said:
OL,13,F"The economics are clear; what is
OL,14,Frequired now is political will ` the
OL,15,Freadiness to take difficult decisions
OL,16,Fon tax and spending in this Budget in
OL,17,Fthe long-term interests of the UK
OL,18,Feconomy."
